usage: uw ecflow realize [-h] [--version] [--config-file PATH]
                         [--output-path PATH] [--scripts-path PATH]
                         [--quiet] [--verbose]

Realize an ecFlow suite definition

Optional arguments:
  -h, --help
      Show help and exit
  --version
      Show version info and exit
  --config-file PATH, -c PATH
      Path to UW YAML config file (default: read from stdin)
  --output-path PATH, -o PATH
      Path to output directory for suite definition (default: write to stdout)
  --scripts-path PATH
      Path to output directory for ecf scripts (default: no scripts generated)
  --quiet, -q
      Print no logging messages
  --verbose, -v
      Print all logging messages
